General.Name: Gold 50 Ltd
General.Description: Gold 50 Limited explores for precious metals in the United States. It primarily explores for gold, silver, and zinc deposits. The company's flagship property is the Golconda project located in Arizona. It also holds interests in the Spitfire, Broken Hills, Top Gun, and Caisson projects situated in central Nevada. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in North Sydney, Australia.
General.Address: 140 Arthur Street, North Sydney, NSW, Australia, 2060
